datalog_actions: can_write(S, M) :- pc_member(S), meeting(M), is_subreviewer(S).
can_delete(S, R) :- PC_Member(S), MeetingPaperResource(R), role(S, "pc-member"), resource_id(R, "pcmember_assignmentcount_rc"), action(S, "delete").
can_delete(S, MP) :- PC_Member(S), MeetingPaper(MP), role(S, "pc-member"), isEq_meetingPaper_resId(MP, "pcmember_conflicts_rc").

datalog_relationships:
has_role(S, pc_member) :- Subject(S).
has_conflict_status(S, subreviewer) :- Subject(S).
has_resource_attribute(R, pcmember_conflicts_rc) :- Resource(R).
datalog_actions: can_access(S, write, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, pc_member), has_conflict_status(S, subreviewer), has_resource_attribute(R, pcmember_conflicts_rc).
can_access(U) :- User(U), has_role(U, 'subreviewer'), has_conflict(U, 'pc_member').
can_delete(S, O) :- Subject(S), Object(O), has_role(S, "pc-member"), has_isConflicted(S, "subreviewer").
can_write(S) :- AccessSubject(S), has_role(S, pc_member).
can_access(S, R, delete) :- pc_member(S), resource(R). can_access(S, R, write) :- pc_member(S), resource(R).
can_delete(S) :- Subject(S), role(S, "subreviewer").
can_write(S, R) :- pc_member(S), resource(R).

datalog_relationships:
has_role(S, 'pc-member') :- Subject(S).
is_subreviewer(S, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R).
datalog_actions: deny_access(S, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, 'pc-member'), is_subreviewer(S, R).
deny_access(S) :- PC_Member(S), is_conflicted(S).

has_role(U, 'subreviewer') :- User(U).

datalog_actions: can_access(U, P) :- User(U), Paper(P), has_role(U, 'subreviewer'), not has_conflict(U, P).
deny_access(S) :- Subject(S), is_conflicted(S).
can_access(S, O, "write") :- Subject(S), Object(O), has_role(S, "pc-member").

datalog_relationships: has_role(S, 'pc-member') :- Subject(S). is_subreviewer(S, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R).
datalog_actions: can_write(S, R) :- Subject(S), Resource(R), has_role(S, 'pc-member'), is_subreviewer(S, R).
deny_all :- false.
can_delete(S) :- Subject(S), role(S, "pc-member"), isMeeting(S, "subreviewer").
can_access(S, O, write) :- Subject(S), Object(O), has_role(S, pc_member).

can_delete(S) :- pc_member(S).
